# Create the first database
when logging into the server # 0.0.0.0:8069
you will find
_____________________________________________________________________________________________
                              Create Database                                               |                                        
_____________________________________________________________________________________________
Master Password = in the beginning , odoo will give you the master password and you can change it for the first time ex 1234 ,and in the end you will be prompted for that password
__________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
Database Name = you can choose any name you want
__________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
Email = Enter any email address you have preferably giving it the vaule Admin
__________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
Password = Enter any Password you have preferably giving it the vaule Admin
__________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
Phone Number = you can put a value or not
__________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
Language = the language you want the adtabase to be composed of
__________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
Country = the country you will choose is the country within which the accounting tree will be formed for example if you choose egypt the will be automatically installed in the accounting module.
__________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
then press continue                                                                                          
